Business Brief -- American Telephone  Telegraph:
   Company Joins in Venture
   That Provides Export Data
The database, which includes up-to-date information on 50
key industries of all major trading partners of the U.S., is
accessed through a toll-free number, 1-800-USA-XPORT, 24
hours a day. By calling the number, callers can receive the
menu and codes of the available countries and industries.
They then can use their fax machine to send the
country/industry codes of their choice to a designated
telephone number, and receive by return fax customized
reports in minutes. The typical report is five to 10 pages
long.